GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 28th May, 2009
5
In continuation of Cabinet Secretariat O.M. of even number dated 23rd May,
2009, the undersigned is directed to inform that in addition to the portfolios already
allocated, as intimated vide Cabinet Secretariat O.M. under reference, other portfolios
have been allocated to the members of the Council of Ministers as shown in Annex-l.
2. The Ministries/Departments that have remained un-allocated, will be looked
after by the Prime Minister.
3. The consolidated list of portfolios of all the members of the Council of Ministers
is at Annex-II.
